Turbotext — Third-Party Attribution
====================================

This project includes ideas/approaches inspired by third-party open-source work:

- Groq chat-completions rewriting approach: inspired by QuickDictate-1
  (https://github.com/KevM90/QuickDictate-1), licensed under the MIT License.
  QuickDictate-1 is an independent fork of cmagnussen/blitztext-app (the same
  upstream project this repository originates from); see
